=== 销量与订阅量 ===

在《重生之境》发行一周时，PS3版登上日本销量榜单第二位，实体版本售出18.4万套<ref name="JapanSales">{{cite web |url=http://gematsu.com/2013/09/media-create-sales-82613-9113 |title=Media Create Sales: 8/26/13 – 9/1/13 |author=Sal Romano, Sal |publisher=Gematsu |date=2013-09-04 |accessdate=2015-12-07 |archive-date=2013-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130907021949/http://gematsu.com/2013/09/media-create-sales-82613-9113 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第二天，在宣布游戏维护时段之后，游戏同时联机数达到32.5万，估计每台服务器约7,000人<ref name="Record">{{cite web |url=http://www.dualshockers.com/2013/09/05/final-fantasy-xiv-solves-problems-gets-325000-concurrent-connections-server-transfers-and-afk-timer-planned/ |title=Final Fantasy XIV Solves Problems, Gets 325,000 Concurrent Connections, Server Transfers and AFK Timer Planned |author=Nelva, Giuseppe |publisher=DualShockers |date=2013-09-05 |accessdate=2015-12-07 |archive-date=2016-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022215234/http://www.dualshockers.com/2013/09/05/final-fantasy-xiv-solves-problems-gets-325000-concurrent-connections-server-transfers-and-afk-timer-planned/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。吉田直树在[[东京电玩展|东京电玩展]]上制作人来信LIVE中宣布，游戏已经有100万独立订阅者<ref name="MillionSubscribers">{{cite web|url=http://www.dualshockers.com/2013/09/21/tgs-2013-final-fantasy-xiv-has-over-a-million-players-info-and-relevant-screencaps-from-the-live-letter/|title=TGS 2013: Final Fantasy XIV Has Over a Million Players: Info and Relevant Screencaps from the Live Letter|author=Giuseppe Nelva|publisher=DualShockers|date=2013-09-21|accessdate=2015-12-07|archive-date=2016-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022215232/http://www.dualshockers.com/2013/09/21/tgs-2013-final-fantasy-xiv-has-over-a-million-players-info-and-relevant-screencaps-from-the-live-letter/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。到2014年2月时，有180万玩家创建了670万名角色，记录的游戏时间达到4亿小时<ref>{{cite web |author=Kollar, Philip |url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/2/13/5405344/final-fantasy-14s-playstation-4-launch-is-just-the-start-for-naoki |title=Final Fantasy 14's PlayStation 4 launch is just the start for Naoki Yoshida |publisher=Polygon |date=2014-02-13 |accessdate=2015-12-07 |archive-date=2021-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115060502/https://www.polygon.com/2014/2/13/5405344/final-fantasy-14s-playstation-4-launch-is-just-the-start-for-naoki |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2014年4月16日，史克威尔艾尼克斯宣布注册游戏的帐号已超过200万<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/215568/Latest_Final_Fantasy_XIV_figures_500K_registrations_in_6_months.php|title=Latest Final Fantasy XIV figures: 500K registrations in 6 months|last=Rose|first=Mike|date=2014-04-16|work=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|publisher=Think Services|accessdate=2014-04-16|archive-date=2019-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191202165901/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/215568/Latest_Final_Fantasy_XIV_figures_500K_registrations_in_6_months.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2014年12月达到250万，2015年2月突破400万<ref>{{cite web |url=http://newgame.duowan.com/1502/288973185041.html |title=SE宣布《最终幻想14》全球注册用户已达400万 |publisher=多玩游戏 |date=2015-02-27 |accessdate=2015-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017041553/http://newgame.duowan.com/1502/288973185041.html |archive-date=2015-10-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。截至2016年7月，游戏的玩家数量总计超过了600万人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/2/5/5381734/square-enix-q3-2014-earnings-returning-to-profitability|title=Square Enix returning to profitability in 2014 fiscal year|accessdate=2015-12-07|author=Sarkar, Samit|date=2014-02-05|publisher=Polygon|archive-date=2014-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140428184008/http://www.polygon.com/2014/2/5/5381734/square-enix-q3-2014-earnings-returning-to-profitability|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2021年12月，全球注册用户累計已超過2500万個<ref name="r18m">{{Cite web |url=https://www.famitsu.com/news/202112/02243178.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-12-03 |archive-date=2021-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211203052151/https://www.famitsu.com/news/202112/02243178.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》母公司[[Enterbrain|Enterbrain]]收集的2013年度日本零售软件销量前100名榜单“Fami通2013年Top 100”中，PS3版《最终幻想XIV：重生之境》以244,574份的日本实体销量排名第32名<ref>{{cite web|url= http://nintendoeverything.com/famitsu-top-100-best-selling-games-of-2013-thus-far/|title= Famitsu: Top 100 best-selling games of 2013 thus far|publisher= Nintendo Everything|date= 2013-07-27|accessdate= 2015-12-07|archive-date= 2021-03-10|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210310072047/https://nintendoeverything.com/famitsu-top-100-best-selling-games-of-2013-thus-far/|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

